search_term: Find the official pricing page URL for Acuity Scheduling (acuity-scheduling.com). Only provide the exact URL to the pricing page, not a summary of pricing information.
response_text: The official URL for Acuity Scheduling's pricing page is: https://acuityscheduling.com/signup
